{"tid":371812,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"搞清楚啦，香港從來都唔係同澳門同一陣線囉","createTime":"2017-08-24T02:02:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-24T03:22:07.000Z","uid":34676,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fec4db5c024aa9589a287fcd53d1cb6cb98611b5","tid":371812,"uid":34676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T02:02:46.000Z","msg":"屌你老母打個風又突然一家親<br />\n平時澳狗又寸寸貢一副嘴臉<br />\n打風就話人冇同理心<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n抵撚死啦澳門狗，仲有你呢啲唔撚係天災囉，係人禍啊，由頭到尾都係你地班澳門狗自己人殺自己人，咎由自取，做咩唔笑得？就算香港他朝一樣，其他人都有恥笑既權利，但我今日就笑鳩你班澳門狗先<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n澳門人，今次你地殺左幾多自己友啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42ce197bbbd7a0892eeb568852e39b058be87957","tid":371812,"uid":34676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T02:07:47.000Z","msg":"識你老鼠咩澳門狗，上嚟認親認戚，有撚種唔好過嚟，屈喺澳門到做狗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f659ae76ad8d2148ed6a1c046842c3b64e5e2240","tid":371812,"uid":41201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T03:22:07.000Z","msg":"港人口口聲聲憎支那，出國旅遊出事咪又係搵中國領事館<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}